Chris Ball made the heartbreaking final goodbye video to his family before taking his own life on September 14 last year .
His brother Jayden found his body along with a USB stick on top of a piece of paper which simply said: 'Mum and Dad, please watch'
His family have shared the heartbreaking video publicly to raise awareness of the crippling disease .
It is part of a petition to call for more beds for suicidal youths in hospitals .